rows.label: tlk70000018_03_msg0001
rows.name:
Ho there, fancy seeing you again!
Me? I'm just having a staring contest
with these here fish. Heh.

rows.label: tlk70000018_03_msg0002
rows.name:
Wh-what? You're saying I should just
go home already? W-well...

rows.label: tlk70000018_03_msg0003
rows.name:
To tell the truth, my wife was pretty
vexed with me for up and leaving
without a word of thanks for you guys...

rows.label: tlk70000018_03_msg0004
rows.name:
I'm happy to be back in the city, I really
am... But I think I'd like to let things, er,
cool off a bit at home first. Heh.
